Audit Conclusion
================================================================================
Overall Status: Foundation is solid; production readiness is blocked primarily by content completion and profile-aware publication automation.

Immediate Priority Order
1. Replace placeholders with real, outcome-focused content.
2. Implement profile-aware build/output path.
3. Add CI quality gates (schema validation + ATS extraction + placeholder linting).
